action
  KEY                    TYPE    ENUM  SCOPES     DEFAULT  HELP
  actions_enabled        bool          admin:box           Whether the action plane is enabled.
  action_reverse_secret  secret        admin:box           Reverse-channel HMAC secret (write-only).

kb
  KEY       TYPE  ENUM                               SCOPES        DEFAULT  HELP
  provider  enum  intercom|supporthero|knowledgeowl  config:write           KB provider.
  base_url  url                                      config:write           KB API base URL.

settings
  KEY           TYPE   ENUM              SCOPES        DEFAULT     HELP
  max_run_usd   float                    config:write  1           Per-run cost-cap base in USD.
  default_tier  enum   standard|pro|max  config:write  standard    Default model ladder rung.
  image_model   model                    config:write  vendor/img  Image-describe model override.
